					"type": 23,
					"value": "goto -150; 31; 18, ctrl-k Arabella to kill her and test SWD.\r\nAlternatively, go to -150; 31; 18, speak with Arabella, say that you aren't going to help her. She will disappear out of sight - then go to-157; 21; -85, find her corpse and SwD"
				},
